FAQ
How's the domain created ?
Each domain is a NFT minted by the nodes on blockchain to the domain owner
Do I need to renew the domain?
No. NBdomain is permanent. Once you own the domain, it will be yours until you transfer/sale to others
How to build apps that support NBdomain?
Please checkout doc.nbdomain.com
What wallet can be used to operate NBdomain?
You can use the VBox wallet in Maxthon browser: maxthon.com .
